room_title: Escape room "Oddities Shoppe" by Mission Escape Rooms in Gambrills
room_address: 1405 S. Main Chapel Way, Suite 105 Gambrills, MD 21054
room_description:
While strolling down the main drag late one evening, you notice that only one shop on the whole street still has the “open” sign buzzing. Curious, you peek through the faded window and glimpse the silhouette of a man pacing erratically through the cluttered aisles of his shop. Trying the door, you find that it creaks open at a mere touch, and you see yourself inside.
Within, you discover that the shop is filled with odd and slightly unsettling trinkets for sale. After a brief stroll through this bizarre bazaar, you are somehow unable to locate the shopkeeper. With a chill, you decide that this place is a bit too strange for your taste. Making your mind up, you go to leave; only to find that the door has locked and you’re stuck in this dank and musty oddities shop…
